403
00:17:02.647 --> 00:17:05.274  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:15.00%  line:89.66% 
[ Sighs ]

404
00:17:06.692 --> 00:17:08.986  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
Listen, you always say
express your feelings.

405
00:17:09.070 --> 00:17:11.029  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
When I get mad,
that’s what I do.

406
00:17:11.113 --> 00:17:14.533  position:55.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:79.00% 
Hello? Yeah, I can talk.
My parents dragged me
into this stupid movie.

407
00:17:14.617 --> 00:17:16.785  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:25.00%  line:69.06% 
<i>♪♪ [ Fanfare ]</i>

408
00:17:14.617 --> 00:17:16.785  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:84.23% 
Go ahead, Jay.
Feed him his phone.

409
00:17:16.869 --> 00:17:18.453  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
You’re telling me
that doesn’t bother you?

410
00:17:18.537 --> 00:17:20.247  position:10.00%,start  align:start size:85.00%  line:84.33% 
